Nalaureth, you will get zero headway with Triton or any other long established guilds on Povar with your calendar idea.  I won't  go into the details on this with you since Rombus covered it.<P>I would suggest that if you get a bunch of peeps together to do a raid, and the place you had planned is "occupied" then take your crew and find another place to raid.  There are a ton of places to go now and with porters it takes very little time to move a raid party around.  It's no different than finding frenzy camped in lguk and then heading to an open camp.  There's just more people involved.  <IMG SRC="smile.gif" border="0">  And yes, our plans occasionally get foiled too so being uber doesn't make you magically immune.  We just go do something else.
