<IMG SRC="http://www.tritonguild.com/tritonforum/profile_ubb6.gif" BORDER="0" ALT="Profile for Nalaureth"></A>  &nbsp;  &nbsp;&nbsp;<A HREF="http://www.tritonguild.com/cgi-bin/triton/ultimatebb.cgi?ubb=edit_post&f=1&t=001131&reply_num=000027&u=00001160"><IMG SRC="http://www.tritonguild.com/tritonforum/edit_ubb6.gif" BORDER="0" ALT="Edit/Delete Post"></A> &nbsp;&nbsp;<A HREF="http://www.tritonguild.com/cgi-bin/triton/ultimatebb.cgi?ubb=reply&f=1&t=001131&replyto=000027"><IMG SRC="http://www.tritonguild.com/tritonforum/quote_ubb6.gif" BORDER="0" ALT="Reply With Quote"></A>
