Reservations dont work, we dont have scedule with ra, we have a rotation.  We take turns on mobs, or if other dont have people to kill we'll kill.  Its easier for us because we compete for the mobs.<BR>Letting other people we dont know come into fear with us, causes problems.  You get noobs in the zone who dont know how to assist/not train us/know how to play and it causes problems.  Having people lag us or crowd us makes us kill slower.  When we raid we go in kill the shit and get out fast as we can, having you guys come in slows us down.<BR>Steamrolling would have been if you guys were about to zone into fear and we ran right over you and did fear anyway.  <BR>Fear repops everyday, shit happens get over it.  You had to change your fear raid because we were there first, go raid somewhere else.  When that shit happens to us, we dont steamroll, we dont go post on their boards whining, we dont get pissy about it, we go raid something else.<P>--------------------<P> <IMG SRC="http://wots-signatures.hypermart.net/saosig.gif"> 
